View Member's: Reviews Ordered by telephone & service was good. Decided to return the item as it was not really what we wanted; spec was too low. Contacted retailer by telephone and was given return ref number and full address to send item back to. Asked for e-mail confirmation that my credit card had been refunded and this was sent within 48 hours of posting back the item. All in all, very good service received with no quibbles about returning the item & getting a full refund. Retailer Response (11/10/07): We are not quite sure why we were only rated with 3 stars here as we did provide as quoted \\\"All in all, very good service received with no quibbles about returning the item & getting a full refund\\\" All done as soon as the customer decided he did not want the product, with no costs charged to the customer! Overall Rating
